problem.script:
from mitxgraders import *

grader = MatrixGrader(
    answers={
        'comparer_params': [
            '[[1, x], [x, -1]]',
            'sqrt(1+x^2)'
        ],
        'comparer': eigenvector_comparer
    },
    variables=['x'],
    max_array_dim=2
)

problem.p:
Enter an eigenvector of \(
  \begin{bmatrix}
    1 & x \\
    x & -1
  \end{bmatrix}
\) with positive eigenvalue.
